Package ie.atu.sw.wordembedding

Record Class WordEmbeddingMap

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
ie.atu.sw.wordembedding.WordEmbeddingMap
Record Components:
wordEmbeddingMap - the map of words to their corresponding embeddings
All Implemented Interfaces:
WordEmbeddingMapInterface
public record WordEmbeddingMap(Map<String,WordEmbedding> wordEmbeddingMap) extends Record implements WordEmbeddingMapInterface
Record representing a map of words to their embeddings and implementing WordEmbeddingMapInterface. Provides methods to interact with the word embeddings, such as loading from a file and retrieving embeddings.
